    "body": "I have a function which I plan to revert, since the REVERT instruction provides a way to stop execution and revert state changes, without consuming all provided gas and with the ability to return a reason. At the same time, I want to get the trace of the transaction, can we do that?\r\n\r\n```\r\nfunction attack1_int_overflow() public {\r\n        multiVulnToken.transferProxy(\r\n            address(this),\r\n            attacker1Address,\r\n            uint256(2 ** 255 + 1),\r\n            uint256(2 ** 255)\r\n        );\r\n        revert();\r\n    }\r\n```",
